          <enum>(2)</enum>
          <text>in<cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Social Security Act/s:1886/ss:d/p:5/sp:G/cl:ii/scl:II">clause
			 (ii)(II)</cato:entity-ref>, by striking<quote>October 1, 2013</quote>and inserting<quote>October 1, 2014</quote>.</text>
        </paragraph>
      </subsection>
