              <cato:entity-ref entity-type="act" value="Social Security Act/s:1886/ss:b/p:3/sp:D">Section 1886(b)(3)(D) of the Social Security Act</cato:entity-ref>(<external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/42/1395ww">
