            <text>in<cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Social Security Act/s:1886/ss:b/p:3/sp:D/cl:iv">clause (iv)</cato:entity-ref>, by
			 striking<quote>through fiscal year 2013</quote>and inserting<quote>through
			 fiscal year 2014</quote>.</text>
